# Stage 00 — recon (L2)

Initial reconnaissance of the project. Detects workspace type (greenfield, existing, external_repo), validates coherence between declared profile/tier and the actual repository state, lists active ADRs and inheritable lessons. Output feeds discovery (stage 01) with a factual baseline — no invented context that is not in the FS.

